{"tid":416182,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人想自己消失係呢個世界","createTime":"2017-09-27T14:46:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T15:55:20.000Z","uid":65439,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a384d4b4a145619252cc43a58da46e9ada53de20","tid":416182,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:46:34.000Z","msg":"好似所有野都唔合自己心意<br />\n例如友情家庭未來<br />\n<br />\n其中好似我最在意既朋友咁 我曾經好重視佢哋<br />\n但係最後發現原來我係可有可無<br />\n或者更甚係阻住佢哋 拒絕我去容入佢哋<br />\n<br />\n直到依家我對所有野都好似唔care咁<br />\n不斷係到諗 &ldquo;做左又點&rdquo; &ldquo;有咩用&rdquo;<br />\n覺得存在係度唔知做咩<br />\n就算呢一刻突然消失都冇感覺<br />\n成個人好似掘空左咁<br />\n有冇巴打都係咁"},{"pid":"72fc1d36b8e2d136c28ecb82dcfd0a5793f91580","tid":416182,"uid":32128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:51:16.000Z","msg":"日日都咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9dae57ec05cae364318a4e0275a44fa8aff482d","tid":416182,"uid":65439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:53:21.000Z","msg":"好想離開同消失<br />\n見到呢個世界就覺得好攰"},{"pid":"a82fb117eba362e904e01c1dab1841a5d03b10ec","tid":416182,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:53:28.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"4bf24bd652103c694f0678b97acf446808c956bb","tid":416182,"uid":64944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:06:22.000Z","msg":"唔撚想番工呀屌<br />\n點解唔車死我呀"},{"pid":"3e7bf21688f561bcdb7837bbcd40231181ff4afe","tid":416182,"uid":24982,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:07:20.000Z","msg":"唔想生存 但又唔想身邊嘅人唔開心<br />\n想從來都無出世"},{"pid":"47a9fc15a1a69f8dc267e06e81db18491b27d7e9","tid":416182,"uid":54387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:27:34.000Z","msg":"樓主=我"},{"pid":"201d8c2223987a11af72156946c89e2c1eac4974","tid":416182,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:31:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主=我</blockquote>"},{"pid":"070